textAfterTable: Profile BlackRock Pennsylvania Municipal Bond Fund is an open-end fund incorporated in the USA. The Fund's aim is to provide income exempt from Federal income tax and Pennsylvania personal income taxes. The Fund invests primarily in long-term investment grade Pennsylvania municipal bonds.
